---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — AI Zest" description="AI Zest is a curated directory of the best AI tools. We review, compare, and rank AI tools to help you find the perfect tool for your needs.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#3B82F6]">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">About</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">About AI Zest</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        AI Zest is a curated directory of the best AI tools available in 2026. We review, compare, 
        and rank AI tools across every category — from writing assistants to image generators, 
        from coding copilots to video creators.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>
        We help you discover the right AI tool for your needs. With thousands of AI tools launching 
        every month, finding the right one is harder than ever. We test them so you don't have to.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Our Reviews</h2>
      <p>Every tool on AI Zest is evaluated based on:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Feature completeness and quality</li>
        <li>Pricing and value for money</li>
        <li>Ease of use</li>
        <li>Customer reviews and reputation</li>
        <li>Regular updates and improvements</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question, suggestion, or want to submit a tool for review? 
        Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:admin@aizest.net">admin@aizest.net</a>.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        Some of the links on this website are affiliate links. If you click through and make a 
        purchase, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us maintain 
        and grow AI Zest. Our reviews remain unbiased — we only recommend tools we genuinely believe in.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
